	<h1 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl text-left block  border-b-2 py-14 p-10 pl-0 border-solid border-black">Зачем использовать Markdown?</h1>
	<div class="py-4">
		<a href="/courses/">Курсы</a> <span class="px-2">/</span> <a href="/courses/markdown/">Markdown</a> <span class="px-2">/</span> <a href="/courses/markdown/getting-started/">Введение</a>
